{"sections":[{"image":"ic_theme_intro.png","backgroundImage":"ic_theme_intro.png","kind":"hero","chapter":"Go further with more ressources","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you have learned how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and view modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources."}]}],"estimatedTimeInMinutes":10,"title":"Going further with more resources"},{"kind":"tasks","tasks":[{"anchor":"More-resources","title":"More resources","contentSection":[{"kind":"contentAndMedia","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode can use the Swift DocC documentation of OUDS, and this documentation is used to build a static web site."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"But there are also other resources which can be useful for you."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"mediaPosition":"trailing"}],"stepsSection":[{"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The iOS technical documentation is available online. It has been generated from all the Swift DocC documentation written in the Swift Package."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You will find several catalogs (as many as librairies) with details about everyhting: components, tokens, themes, providers, etc."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"step","media":"tutorial-discovery-6-1.png","caption":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can get it at "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/","isActive":true}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"code":null,"runtimePreview":null,"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The whole design system is documented and available online. You can find everything about components, tokens, guidelines and principles of OUDS."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"icon finder","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" i